messages.msg:
We're here to pray with you! Here's a prayer you can use to help combat the spirit of lust:

"Heavenly Father, we come before your throne room today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We pray against the Spirit of lust within our hearts, minds, and bodies. We renounce all sexual sins we have been involved in, including fornication, masturbation, and pornography. We cast out all spirits of perversion and receive the Spirit of holiness in our lives to walk in sexual purity. Fill us with the power of your Holy Spirit, Lord, and help us to overcome the temptations we face. In the name of Jesus Christ, we pray. Amen."

If you have any specific requests or need further support, feel free to share!
